  How to Use

  1. Install dependencies

  pip install -r requirements.txt --break-system-packages

  2. Prepare your data

  Organize in training_data/images/ and training_data/excel/, then:
  python finetune/prepare_dataset.py --data_dir ./training_data --output ./training_data/dataset.jsonl

  3. Fine-tune

  python finetune/finetune_qlora.py \
      --train_data ./training_data/dataset_train.jsonl \
      --output_dir ./finetuned_model

  4. Run inference

  python finetune/inference_finetuned.py \
      --image ./test.jpg \
      --adapter_path ./finetuned_model

